ass=\"flex items-start gap-4 p-3 rounded-none hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors group/item\" href=\"/ja/track-record/\"><div class=\"mt-0.5 w-8 h-8 bg-slate-50 rounded-none flex items-center justify-center text-slate-400 group-hover/item:bg-indigo-50 group-hover/item:text-indigo-600 transition-colors\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-trending-up w-4 h-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 7h6v6\"></path><path d=\"m22 7-8.5 8.5-5-5L2 17\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"space-y-0.5\"><div class=\"text-[10px] font-black text-slate-900 uppercase tracking-widest\">運用実績</div><div class=\"text-[9px] font-bold text-slate-400\">透明性の高い的中率公開</div></div></a></div></div></div><div class=\"relative py-2 px-4 group\"><div class=\"flex items-center h-full\"><button class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 hover:text-black transition-colors focus:outline-none uppercase py-2 h-full\">パートナー・連携<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down w-3 h-3 transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></button></div><div class=\"absolute top-[80%] left-0 w-64 pt-4 opacity-0 translate-y-2 invisible pointer-events-none group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:translate-y-0 group-hover:visible group-hover:pointer-events-auto transition-all duration-300 z-[999]\"><div class=\"bg-white border border-slate-100 rounded-none shadow-2xl shadow-slate-200/60 overflow-hidden p-2\"><a class=\"flex items-start gap-4 p-3 rounded-none hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors group/item\" href=\"/ja/exchange/\"><div class=\"mt-0.5 w-8 h-8 bg-slate-50 rounded-none flex items-center justify-center text-slate-400 group-hover/item:bg-indigo-50 group-hover/item:text-indigo-600 transition-colors\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-users w-4 h-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2\"></path><path d=\"M16 3.128a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.744\"></path><path d=\"M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87\"></path><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\"></circle></svg></div><div class=\"space-y-0.5\"><div class=\"text-[10px] font-black text-slate-900 uppercase tracking-widest\">パートナー連携</div><div class=\"text-[9px] font-bold text-slate-400\">推奨取引プラットフォーム一覧</div></div></a></div></div></div></nav></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 md:gap-4\"><button class=\"hidden md:flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 border border-slate-200 text-slate-900 text-[11px] font-black shadow-sm uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-globe w-3.5 h-3.5 text-indigo-600\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 2a14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0 20 14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0-20\"></path><path d=\"M2 12h20\"></path></svg>EN</button><div class=\"hidden sm:flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 rounded-none text-[11px] font-black text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest\"><div class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-none bg-emerald-500 animate-pulse\"></div>システム稼動中</div><button class=\"lg:hidden p-2.5 -mr-1 text-slate-900 focus:outline-none hover:bg-slate-50 rounded-none transition-colors\" aria-label=\"Menu\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu w-6 h-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 5h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 12h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 19h16\"></path></svg></button></div></header><main class=\"max-w-[1440px] mx-auto border-x border-slate-100 bg-white min-h-screen\"><header class=\"p-6 md:p-12 lg:p-20 border-b border-slate-100 space-y-16\"><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[10px] font-black text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest hover:text-indigo-600 transition-colors group\" href=\"/ja/exchange/\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4 rotate-180 group-hover:-translate-x-1 transition-transform\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg>パートナー一覧に戻る</a><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center\"><div class=\"space-y-10 text-center lg:text-left\"><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center lg:justify-start gap-4\"><span class=\"px-3 py-1 bg-indigo-50 border border-indigo-100 rounded-none text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-600 uppercase tracking-[0.2em]\">推奨パートナー</span><span class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[10px] font-black text-emerald-500 uppercase tracking-widest\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield w-3.5 h-3.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path></svg>公式検証済み</span></div><h1 class=\"text-3xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black text-slate-900 tracking-tighter leading-none font-sans uppercase\">マネックス証券 FXPLUS</h1></div><p class=\"text-sm md:text-base font-bold text-slate-500 max-w-xl mx-auto lg:mx-0 leading-relaxed uppercase border-l-2 border-slate-100 pl-4 md:pl-8\">クリーンな運営と高度な分析ツール。米国株との連携も強力な総合証券。<!-- --> <!-- -->当プラットフォームとAI連携することで、ミリ秒レベルの約定データと高度なセンチメント分析を統合。プロフェッショナルな取引環境を実現します。</p><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center gap-4 justify-center lg:justify-start\"><a target=\"_blank\" class=\"w-full sm:w-auto px-12 py-5 bg-indigo-600 text-white text-[11px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] rounded-none hover:bg-black transition-all shadow-2xl shadow-indigo-100 hover:translate-y-[-2px]\" href=\"https://h.accesstrade.net/sp/cc?rk=0100pldr00oow9\">公式サイトへ</a></div></div><div class=\"bg-white border border-slate-100 p-8 md:p-12 rounded-none shadow-sm space-y-8 flex flex-col items-center\"><div class=\"text-[10px] font-black tracking-[0.3em] text-slate-300 uppercase w-full\">総合評価指標</div><div class=\"relative w-full aspect-square max-w-[400px] mx-auto flex items-center justify-center\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 300 300\" class=\"w-full h-full drop-shadow-sm\"><polygon points=\"150,129 169.97218684219823,143.5106431181261 162.34349029814194,166.9893568818739 137.65650970185806,166.9893568818739 130.02781315780177,143.5106431181261\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#f1f5f9\" stroke-width=\"1\"></polygon><polygon points=\"150,108 189.94437368439645,137.0212862362522 174.68698059628386,183.9787137637478 125.31301940371614,183.9787137637478 110.05562631560355,137.02128623625222\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#f1f5f9\" stroke-width=\"1\"></polygon><polygon points=\"150,87 209.91656052659468,130.53192935437832 187.0304708944258,200.96807064562168 112.9695291055742,200.96807064562168 90.08343947340532,130.53192935437832\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#f1f5f9\" stroke-width=\"1\"></polygon><polygon points=\"150,66 229.8887473687929,124.04257247250442 199.37396119256775,217.95742752749558 100.62603880743227,217.95742752749558 70.1112526312071,124.04257247250443\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#f1f5f9\" stroke-width=\"1\"></polygon><polygon points=\"150,45 249.8609342109911,117.55321559063051 211.71745149070966,234.94678440936949 88.28254850929034,234.94678440936949 50.13906578900887,117.55321559063054\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#f1f5f9\" stroke-width=\"1\"></polygon><line x1=\"150\" y1=\"150\" x2=\"150\" y2=\"45\" stroke=\"#f1f5f9\" stroke-width=\"1\"></line><line x1=\"150\" y1=\"150\" x2=\"249.8609342109911\" y2=\"117.55321559063051\" stroke=\"#f1f5f9\" stroke-width=\"1\"></line><line x1=\"150\" y1=\"150\" x2=\"211.71745149070966\" y2=\"234.94678440936949\" stroke=\"#f1f5f9\" stroke-width=\"1\"></line><line x1=\"150\" y1=\"150\" x2=\"88.28254850929034\" y2=\"234.94678440936949\" stroke=\"#f1f5f9\" stroke-width=\"1\"></line><line x1=\"150\" y1=\"150\" x2=\"50.13906578900887\" y2=\"117.55321559063054\" stroke=\"#f1f5f9\" stroke-width=\"1\"></line><polygon points=\"150,61.8 239.874840789892,120.79789403156747 200.60831022238193,219.65636321568297 90.75124656891873,231.5489130329947 58.127940525888164,120.14895834338009\" fill=\"rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.05)\" stroke=\"#818cf8\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"animate-in fade-in zoom-in duration-1000\"></polygon><circle cx=\"150\" cy=\"61.8\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#818cf8\" class=\"drop-shadow-sm\"></circle><circle cx=\"239.874840789892\" cy=\"120.79789403156747\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#818cf8\" class=\"drop-shadow-sm\"></circle><circle cx=\"200.60831022238193\" cy=\"219.65636321568297\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#818cf8\" class=\"drop-shadow-sm\"></circle><circle cx=\"90.75124656891873\" cy=\"231.5489130329947\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#818cf8\" class=\"drop-shadow-sm\"></circle><circle cx=\"58.127940525888164\" cy=\"120.14895834338009\" r=\"3\" fill=\"#818cf8\" class=\"drop-shadow-sm\"></circle><text x=\"150\" y=\"25\" text-anchor=\"middle\" dominant-baseline=\"central\" class=\"text-[10px] font-black fill-slate-400 uppercase tracking-tighter\">コスト</text><text x=\"273.63734711837\" y=\"111.37287570313157\" text-anchor=\"middle\" dominant-baseline=\"central\" class=\"text-[10px] font-black fill-slate-400 uppercase tracking-tighter\">ツール</text><text x=\"226.41208279802152\" y=\"251.12712429686843\" text-anchor=\"middle\" dominant-baseline=\"central\" class=\"text-[10px] font-black fill-slate-400 uppercase tracking-tighter\">約定力</text><text x=\"73.58791720197851\" y=\"251.12712429686843\" text-anchor=\"middle\" dominant-baseline=\"central\" class=\"text-[10px] font-black fill-slate-400 uppercase tracking-tighter\">安全性</text><text x=\"26.362652881630027\" y=\"111.3728757031316\" text-anchor=\"middle\" dominant-baseline=\"central\" class=\"text-[10px] font-black fill-slate-400 uppercase tracking-tighter\">サポート</text></svg></div><div class=\"flex items-end gap-2 w-full justify-center\"><span class=\"text-4xl font-black tracking-tighter text-slate-900 font-sans\">4.5</span><span class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-300 mb-1\">/ 5.0</span></div></div></div></header><section class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-px bg-slate-100 border-b border-slate-100\"><div class=\"bg-slate-50/50 p-12 md:p-16 space-y-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-target w-5 h-5 text-indigo-600\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"6\"></circle><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"2\"></circle></svg><h3 class=\"text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-slate-400\">推奨される投資家プロファイル</h3></div><p class=\"text-xl font-black text-slate-900 uppercase tracking-tighter leading-tight\">米国株・投資信託も並行して行いたい兼業投資家</p><p class=\"text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 leading-relaxed uppercase border-l-2 border-indigo-100 pl-6\">各ブローカーの約定アルゴリズムとインフラ構成をAIが解析。このサービスは、上記の特性を持つ投資スタイルにおいて最も高いパフォーマンスを発揮します。</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-12 md:p-16 space-y-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-zap w-5 h-5 text-indigo-600\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-slate-400\">AIアドバンテージ</h3></div><p class=\"text-xl font-black text-indigo-600 uppercase tracking-tighter leading-tight\">高度な分析ツールと、FX以外の資産運用も一元管理したい方に最適。</p><p class=\"text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 leading-relaxed uppercase border-l-2 border-slate-100 pl-6\">Synapse Capital&#x27;s AIシグナルと連携することで、期待値の高いエントリーポイントでの滑りを最小限に抑え、戦略の再現性を最大化します。</p></div></section><section class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-px bg-slate-100\"><div class=\"bg-white p-12 md:p-20 space-y-12\"><div class=\"space-y-4\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-black text-emerald-500 tracking-tight flex items-center gap-3 uppercase font-sans\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-8 h-8\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg>主要なメリット</h2><p class=\"text-xs font-black text-slate-300 uppercase tracking-widest\">当AIチームが推奨する主要な強み</p></div><ul class=\"space-y-10\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-6 group\"><div class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 mt-2 bg-emerald-500 rounded-none shrink-0\"></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><p class=\"text-sm font-black text-slate-900 uppercase tracking-tight leading-tight\">分析ツールの質が高い</p><p class=\"text-[11px] font-bold text-slate-400 leading-relaxed uppercase\">業界最狭水準のスプレッドと高度な約定アルゴリズムにより、AIシグナルの再現性を極限まで高めることが可能です。短期売買から。長期保有まで幅広く対応。</p></div></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-6 group\"><div class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 mt-2 bg-emerald-500 rounded-none shrink-0\"></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><p class=\"text-sm font-black text-slate-900 uppercase tracking-tight leading-tight\">大手ネット証券の安心感</p><p class=\"text-[11px] font-bold text-slate-400 leading-relaxed uppercase\">業界最狭水準のスプレッドと高度な約定アルゴリズムにより、AIシグナルの再現性を極限まで高めることが可能です。短期売買から。長期保有まで幅広く対応。</p></div></li></ul></div><div class=\"bg-white p-12 md:p-20 space-y-12 border-l border-slate-100\"><div class=\"space-y-4\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-black text-rose-500 tracking-tight flex items-center gap-3 uppercase font-sans\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-x w-8 h-8\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m15 9-6 6\"></path><path d=\"m9 9 6 6\"></path></svg>リスクと留意点</h2><p class=\"text-xs font-black text-slate-300 uppercase tracking-widest\">留意すべきリスク項目</p></div><ul class=\"space-y-10\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-6 group\"><div class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 mt-2 bg-rose-500 rounded-none shrink-0\"></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><p class=\"text-sm font-black text-slate-900 uppercase tracking-tight leading-tight\">スプレッドが特化型より広い</p><p class=\"text-[11px] font-bold text-slate-400 leading-relaxed uppercase\">高い機能性の一方で、高負荷時のレスポンス低下や、一定の取引コストが発生する場合があります。個別の投資目的に応じて十分に検討してください。</p></div></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-6 group\"><div class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 mt-2 bg-rose-500 rounded-none shrink-0\"></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><p class=\"text-sm font-black text-slate-900 uppercase tracking-tight leading-tight\">アプリが少し重い</p><p class=\"text-[11px] font-bold text-slate-400 leading-relaxed uppercase\">高い機能性の一方で、高負荷時のレスポンス低下や、一定の取引コストが発生する場合があります。個別の投資目的に応じて十分に検討してください。</p></div></li></ul></div></section><section class=\"p-12 md:p-24 bg-white text-center space-y-12\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 px-3 py-1 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 rounded-none text-[10px] font-black text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest leading-none mx-auto\">公式パートナー検証済み</div><div class=\"space-y-6\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-slate-900 tracking-tighter font-sans uppercase\">最適な環境で取引を開始。</h2><p class=\"text-[11px] font-black text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto uppercase tracking-[0.2em] leading-relaxed\">高度なAI解析エンジンと親和性の高い、プロフェッショナルな取引インフラを認定しています。</p></div><div class=\"flex justify-center\"><a target=\"_blank\" class=\"px-16 py-6 bg-black text-white text-[11px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.3em] rounded-none hover:bg-slate-800 transition-all hover:translate-y-[-2px] shadow-2xl\" href=\"https://h.accesstrade.net/sp/cc?rk=0100pldr00oow9\">キャンペーン詳細を確認する<!-- --> <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4 inline-block ml-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></section></main><footer class=\"bg-slate-50/50 border-t border-slate-100 pt-16 md:pt-32 pb-16 px-6 relative overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute -bottom-1/4 -right-1/4 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-indigo-50/30 rounded-none blur-[120px] pointer-events-none\"></div><div class=\"max-w-[1440px] mx-auto space-y-24 relative z-10\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-16 lg:gap-24\"><div class=\"lg:col-span-5 space-y-12\"><div class=\"space-y-6\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-3 group\" href=\"/ja/\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 bg-black rounded-none flex items-center justify-center text-white shrink-0 group-hover:bg-indigo-600 transiti